{
  "stem": "14251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she herself dressed to the nines, even carried a revolver, had the authority to arrest people on the spot, together with her husband, who was also a Jew.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So there is the ugly side, the seamy side of life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I do like to mention that because that proves an extra jeopardy, your own people-- people like them, there were about five, six of them-- could jeopardize you, in fact, did so, did so in the case of friends of mine who were underground during that same time and did so for my mother and father on one occasion.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But she was known by her looks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She was blonde, gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she was called the Blonde Poison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but my parents knew who that was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were spotted by her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She would sidle up to you and say, I'm also underground, where are you staying?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To get you to admit that you were underground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many people fell for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And many she recognized by looking at their IDs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or maybe their look wasn't real.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they made a decision to send me to East Prussia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Abegg, Elisabeth Abegg, and Hilde-- I presume just the two of them and the people involved to make that happen, people I do not know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The church, there was a church called Bekennende Kirche.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do not know what this means in English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a particular sect.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't anything weird or, or offbeat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It just was not uncommon in Germany, but you know, the things here have different names.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wouldn't know Methodist in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, they must have arranged with the Baroness Von Hulesen, who was living in Hanover, had a big estate in Bloestau, East Prussia, about an hour's train ride, slow train, from Konigsberg.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
